These files should be installed under data/add-ons/Trogdor_The_Burninator, to replace the files of the same name in Glubul's Saga.
See Wesnoth site about how to access add-ons: https://wiki.wesnoth.org/AddonStructure
These files are based on the add-on Glubul's Saga, by Argesilao.
Changes made so far include new map, which has been integrated into the scenarios, some file name changes, and deletions from the scenarios.
